	Alt + Enter - for actions
	F2 - Jump througt the errors
	Alt + 1 - Open tool window
	Esc + To focus back to editor
	Ctrl + E - Opens the list of recent opened files
	Ctrl + B - Go to declarations
	Ctrl + Ctrl - Run anything from anywhere
	Ctrl + Shift + UP/Down - Move code
	Shift + Ctrl + Enter - Auto complete statements
	Ctrl + Alt + L - Format code
	Shift + Ctrl + Alt + T - Refactoring code
	Ctrl + Alt + N - Inline variable
	Shift + Ctrl + A - Tool windows
	Shift + shift - Search everywhere
	Ctrl + Alt + Enter - New line before current
	Alt + J - Select next occurance
	Ctrl + Shift + Alt + J - Select all acurances
